"file_path":"/mZVpPtzfwCFPLum2yetdkUSR5Am.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":1,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":2160,"height":1215,"file_path":"/ojmnHnhwp91xacMiVvRllBK5gVL.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":1,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":2160,"height":1215,"file_path":"/iRrsoLua9QugekZbK31nXE7j0p6.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":1,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/ehZqcU0TnAeKLpZm8q4MyPk0s7j.jpg","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","vote_count":1,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0.166}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T08:07:07.538+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"La Grazia","runtime":133,"tagline":"A president. A pardon. A legacy.","homepage":"","overview":"As his tenure as President of Italy nears its end, Mariano De Santis faces wrenching decisions-both political and deeply personal. Amid these moral quandaries, he must confront his own conscience and seek guidance from those closest to him, including his confidante and daughter, Dorotea."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":133,"tagline":"Di chi sono i nostri giorni?","homepage":"","overview":"Il Presidente della Repubblica Mariano De Santis è ormai anziano e alla fine del suo mandato. Vedovo, ex-giurista e profondamente cattolico, si troverà di fronte a due ultimi dilemmi: se concedere la grazia a due persone che hanno commesso un omicidio in circostanze che potrebbero essere considerate attenuanti o se promulgare la legge sull'eutanasia."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"라 그라찌아","runtime":131,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"황혼기에 접어든 한 남자가 있다. 그는 지나온 삶을 정리하고, 과거와 화해하며, 멀어졌던 자녀들에게 먼저 다가간다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":131,"tagline":"Un président. Une grâce. Un héritage.","homepage":"","overview":"Mariano De Santis, Président de la République italienne, est un homme marqué par le deuil de sa femme et la solitude du pouvoir. Alors que son mandat touche à sa fin, il doit faire face à des décisions cruciales qui l’obligent à affronter ses propres dilemmes moraux : deux grâces présidentielles et un projet de loi hautement controversé."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"恩典","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"马里亚诺·德·桑蒂斯是意大利共和国总统。此人与现实中的任何总统均无关联，完全是作者虚构的人物。他丧偶多年，且信奉天主教，有一个女儿名叫多罗泰亚——和他一样，女儿也是一名法律学者。任期即将结束之际，在波澜不惊的日常中，两项最后的职责摆在了他面前：就两份敏感的总统特赦申请 做出决定。这些抉择构成了真正的道德困境，并且以看似无法理清的方式，与他的私人生活纠缠在了一起。在疑虑的驱使下，他必须做出抉择。而这位杰出的意大利总统，怀着强烈的责任感，必将履行这份职责。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":133,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://mubi.com/de/de/films/la-grazia","overview":"Gegen Ende seiner Amtszeit als Präsident Italiens sieht sich Mariano De Santis mit schwerwiegenden politischen und persönlichen Entscheidungen konfrontiert. Nun muss er sich seinem Gewissen stellen und den Rat jener suchen, die ihm am nächsten stehen, darunter seine Vertraute und Tochter Dorotea."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":131,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://gutekfilm.pl/la-grazia-sorrentino","overview":"Prezydent Mariano De Santis jest już w podeszłym wieku i zbliża się koniec jego kadencji. Wdowiec, były prawnik i pobożny katolik, stanie przed dwoma ostatecznymi dylematami: czy ułaskawić dwie osoby, które popełniły morderstwo w okolicznościach, które można uznać za łagodzące, czy też wprowadzić ustawę o eutanazji."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Başkan Mariano De Santis'in görev süresi sona ermek üzeredir. İnatçı doğası ve siyasete aşırı dikkatli yaklaşımı nedeniyle aşağılayıcı bir şekilde 'Cemento armato' (betonarme) lakabıyla anılan başkan, eşinin yasını tutarak ve hip-hop dinleyerek başkanlık sarayının yankılanan salonlarında yalnızlaşmıştır. Sivil hayata dönmeden önce De Santis, mirasını sağlamlaştıracak bir dizi cesur karar vermek zorundadır: bir çift başkanlık affı ve çığır açan bir politika yasa tasarısı."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Благодать","runtime":0,"tagline":"Президент. Помилування. Спадщина.","homepage":"","overview":"Президент Італії, якого за непохитність прозвали «Залізобетон», проводить останні місяці на посаді. Поважний лідер, що подолав шість державних криз, тепер має три проблемні документи, що чекають його підпису. Це помилування двох засуджених і рішення, яке загрожує розколом суспільства – закон про евтаназію. Якщо підпише останній, стане убивцею, якщо ні – катом. Але найбільше його мучить сорокарічна таємниця: хто був коханцем його покійної дружини?"},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":133,"tagline":"Um presidente. Um indulto. Um legado.","homepage":"https://mubi.com/pt/br/films/la-grazia","overview":"Com seu mandato como Presidente da Itália chegando ao fim, Mariano De Santis enfrenta decisões dilacerantes, tanto políticas quanto profundamente pessoais. Em meio a esses dilemas morais, ele precisa encarar sua consciência e buscar orientação das pessoas mais próximas, incluindo sua filha Dorotea."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":133,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Mariano De Santis, presidente (ficiticio) de la República italiana, es un veterano político demócrata, humanista y católico, que de repente comienza a dudar sobre varias importantes decisiones que debe tomar, en especial sobre si aprueba o no una ley de eutanasia, planteándose un gran dilema moral."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"החסד","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"מריאנו דה סנטיס הוא נשיא הרפובליקה האיטלקית – דמות בדיונית לחלוטין, אלמן ואב לדורותיאה, משפטנית צעירה ההולכת בדרכו. כהונתו מתקרבת לסיומה לאחר שנים של שקט יחסי, אך דווקא אז נוחתות על שולחנו שתי בקשות חנינה רגישות במיוחד, ההופכות לדילמות מוסריות של ממש. אותן דילמות נשזרות בחייו האישיים באופן מפתיע, ומעמידות אותו בפני הכרעות בלתי־אפשריות לכאורה. מה הדבר הנכון לעשות? ואחרי הכל – איך הוא ייזכר בדפי ההיסטוריה?"},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Žēlastība","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Latviešu","iso_639_1":"lv","iso_3166_1":"LV","english_name":"Latvian"},{"data":{"title":"Milost","runtime":131,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Italského prezidenta (Toni Servillo) čekají před odchodem z úřadu poslední těžká rozhodnutí. Na stole má dvě žádosti o milost za vraždy z lásky a jeden kontroverzní zákon. Aby přestal váhat nad správným řešením, musí se nejdřív smířit s nedávným odchodem milované ženy i podezřením, že mu byla nevěrná. Odpověď na tajemství, které mu nedá spát, ale zná jen jeden člověk. Originální drama o lásce, pochybách a odpovědnosti představuje oscarového režiséra Paola Sorrentina (Velká nádhera, Mládí) ve zcela novém světle a životní formě. (Aerofilms)"},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Pe măsură ce mandatul său de președinte al Italiei se apropie de sfârșit, Mariano De Santis se confruntă cu decizii dificile - atât politice, cât și profund personale. În mijlocul acestor dileme morale, el trebuie să-și confrunte propria conștiință și să ceară îndrumare de la cei mai apropiați, inclusiv de la confidenta și fiica sa, Dorotea."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Al acercarse el fin de su mandato como presidente de Italia, Mariano De Santis se enfrenta a decisiones difíciles, tanto políticas como profundamente personales. En medio de estos dilemas morales, debe confrontar su propia conciencia y buscar la guía de sus allegados, incluyendo a su confidente e hija, Dorotea."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Грация","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Президент Италии Мариано де Сантис, осторожный центрист, приближается к концу срока и к почетной пенсии. Дочь, юристка и его ближайшая помощница, кладет на стол Мариано проект закона об эвтаназии, довольно взрывоопасного, учитывая положение Рима в самом сердце католического мира. Еще на президентском столе лежат два прошения о помиловании: одно касается пожилого мужчины, задушившего свою страдавшую болезнью Альцгеймера жену, другое — молодой женщины, зарезавшей мужа-абьюзера."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"恩典","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"馬里亞諾·德·桑蒂斯是義大利共和國總統。此人與現實中的任何總統均無關聯，完全是作者虛構的人物。他喪偶多年，且信奉天主教，有一個女兒名叫多羅泰亞——和他一樣，女兒也是一名法律學者。任期即將結束之際，在波瀾不驚的日常中，兩項最後的職責擺在了他面前：就兩份敏感的總統特赦申請做出決定。這些抉擇構成了真正的道德困境，並且以看似無法理清的方式，與他的私人生活糾纏在了一起。在疑慮的驅使下，他必須做出抉擇。而這位傑出的義大利總統，懷著強烈的責任感，必將履行這份職責。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Milost","runtime":0,"tagline":"Predsednik. Pomilostitev. Zapuščina.","homepage":"","overview":"Predsednik Republike Italije Mariano De Santis se v zadnjih dneh svojega mandata sooča s pomembnimi političnimi in osebnimi odločitvami. Sredi teh moralnih dilem se mora soočiti s svojo vestjo in poiskati nasvet pri najbližjih, vključno s svojo hčerko in zaupnico Doroteo."},"name":"Slovenščina","iso_639_1":"sl","iso_3166_1":"SI","english_name":"Slovenian"},{"data":{"title":"موهبت","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"رئیس‌جمهور بیوهٔ ایتالیا در ماه‌های پایانی دوران ریاست‌جمهوری‌اش، درگیر بحران‌های اخلاقی درباره تصویب قانون اتانازی و بخشش قاتلان می‌شود؛ در حالی که هم‌زمان با حقیقت تلخ خیانت همسرِ فقیدش نیز دست‌وپنجه نرم می‌کند."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"Halastus","runtime":0,"tagline":"President. Armuandmine. Pärand.","homepage":"","overview":"“Halastus” on hinnatud itaalia lavastaja Paolo Sorrentino (“Kohutav ilu”) uus film, mille peategelane on fiktiivne Itaalia president Mariano De Santis. Ta on lesk ja katoliiklane. Tal on tütar Dorotea, kes on pühendunud õigusteadlane nagu mees isegi. Ametiaja lõppedes on tal laual seaduseelnõu ja kaks armuandmispalvet. Need kätkevad endis moraalseid dilemmasid, mis põimuvad tema eraeluga viisil, mida tundub võimatu lahti harutada. Kahtleval presidendil tuleb otsused langetada. Ja sügavast vastutustundest kantuna ta seda ka teeb."},"name":"Eesti","iso_639_1":"et","iso_3166_1":"EE","english_name":"Estonian"},{"data":{"title":"A kegyelem","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Paolo Sorrentino A kegyelem című filmjében ismét a legkedveltebb színészével dolgozott együtt: Toni Servillo ezúttal Olaszország képzeletbeli elnökét kelti életre, aki jogászként rendíthetetlenül hisz a gránitszilárdságú törvényekben. Egész mandátuma alatt végig az elveit követte, utolsó elnöki döntései viszont akár az egész pályafutását átértékelhetik. A nyugdíjhoz közeledve ugyanis két kegyelmi kérvény és egy nagyon megosztó törvényjavaslat kerül az asztalára."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"69937667ceafaf9be5065a6c","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/69937667ceafaf9be5065a6c","author":"badelf","content":"$11","created_at":"2026-02-16T19:56:23.803Z","updated_at":"2026-02-16T19:56:23.823Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":10,"username":"badelf","avatar_path":null}}],"recommendations":[{"id":1265063,"adult":false,"title":"After the Hunt","video":false,"overview":"A college professor finds herself at a personal and professional crossroads when a star pupil levels an accusation against one of her colleagues, and a dark secret from her own past threatens to come to light.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.0927,"vote_count":448,"poster_path":"/ryF8QPGUGlo8gRB4OYKb4J0r3aJ.jpg","release_date":"2025-10-09","vote_average":5.667,"backdrop_path":"/x0J0OMKwnX1eeVRQWeb2D05yd3K.jpg","original_title":"After the Hunt","original_language":"en"},{"id":565770,"adult":false,"title":"Blue Beetle","video":false,"overview":"Recent college grad Jaime Reyes returns home full of aspirations for his future, only to find that home is not quite as he left it. As he searches to find his purpose in the world, fate intervenes when Jaime unexpectedly finds himself in possession of an ancient relic of alien biotechnology: the Scarab.","genre_ids":[28,878,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.4075,"vote_count":3025,"poster_path":"/mXLOHHc1Zeuwsl4xYKjKh2280oL.jpg","release_date":"2023-08-16","vote_average":6.645,"backdrop_path":"/3H9NA1KWEQN0ItL3Wl3SFZYP6yV.jpg","original_title":"Blue Beetle","original_language":"en"},{"id":872585,"adult":false,"title":"Oppenheimer","video":false,"overview":"The story of J. Robert Oppenheimer's role in the development of the atomic bomb during World War II.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":19.7563,"vote_count":11389,"poster_path":"/8Gxv8gSFCU0XGDykEGv7zR1n2ua.jpg","release_date":"2023-07-19","vote_average":8.034,"backdrop_path":"/ycnO0cjsAROSGJKuMODgRtWsHQw.jpg","original_title":"Oppenheimer","original_language":"en"},{"id":264660,"adult":false,"title":"Ex Machina","video":false,"overview":"Caleb, a coder at the world's largest internet company, wins a competition to spend a week at a private mountain retreat belonging to Nathan, the reclusive CEO of the company. But when Caleb arrives at the remote location he finds that he will have to participate in a strange and fascinating experiment in which he must interact with the world's first true artificial intelligence, housed in the body of a beautiful robot girl.","genre_ids":[18,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.7588,"vote_count":14042,"poster_path":"/dmJW8IAKHKxFNiUnoDR7JfsK7Rp.jpg","release_date":"2015-01-21","vote_average":7.573,"backdrop_path":"/uqOuJ50EtTj7kkDIXP8LCg7G45D.jpg","original_title":"Ex Machina","original_language":"en"},{"id":389,"adult":false,"title":"12 Angry Men","video":false,"overview":"The defense and the prosecution have rested and the jury is filing into the jury room to decide if a young Spanish-American is guilty or innocent of murdering his father. What begins as an open and shut case soon becomes a mini-drama of each of the jurors' prejudices and preconceptions about the trial, the accused, and each other.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":12.4833,"vote_count":9766,"poster_path":"/ow3wq89wM8qd5X7hWKxiRfsFf9C.jpg","release_date":"1957-04-10","vote_average":8.556,"backdrop_path":"/w4bTBXcqXc2TUyS5Fc4h67uWbPn.jpg","original_title":"12 Angry Men","original_language":"en"},{"id":68718,"adult":false,"title":"Django Unchained","video":false,"overview":"With the help of a German bounty hunter, a freed slave sets out to rescue his wife from a brutal Mississippi plantation owner.","genre_ids":[18,37],"media_type":"movie","popularity":13.7776,"vote_count":27606,"poster_path":"/7oWY8VDWW7thTzWh3OKYRkWUlD5.jpg","release_date":"2012-12-25","vote_average":8.187,"backdrop_path":"/s4cJQaj40SwMifUrrdtdOJsjnRO.jpg","original_title":"Django Unchained","original_language":"en"},{"id":19995,"adult":false,"title":"Avatar","video":false,"overview":"In the 22nd century, a paraplegic Marine is dispatched to the moon Pandora on a unique mission, but becomes torn between following orders and protecting an alien civilization.","g