-12-19","vote_average":6.994,"backdrop_path":"/evPzxMacNWsjkUKQO4NXKe5Rl6a.jpg","original_title":"Zero Dark Thirty","original_language":"en"},{"id":170,"adult":false,"title":"28 Days Later","video":false,"overview":"Twenty-eight days after a killer virus was accidentally unleashed from a British research facility, a small group of London survivors are caught in a desperate struggle to protect themselves from the infected. Carried by animals and humans, the virus turns those it infects into homicidal maniacs -- and it's absolutely impossible to contain.","genre_ids":[27,53,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":17.7462,"vote_count":8256,"poster_path":"/sQckQRt17VaWbo39GIu0TMOiszq.jpg","release_date":"2002-10-31","vote_average":7.236,"backdrop_path":"/aJFwk1clMal1prxAvKAgHxKPAf.jpg","original_title":"28 Days Later","original_language":"en"},{"id":297222,"adult":false,"title":"PK","video":false,"overview":"A stranger in the city asks questions no one has asked before. Known only by his initials, the man's innocent questions and childlike curiosity take him on a journey of love, laughter and letting go.","genre_ids":[35,18,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.4022,"vote_count":1122,"poster_path":"/z2x2Y4tncefsIU7h82gmUM5vnBJ.jpg","release_date":"2014-12-18","vote_average":7.698,"backdrop_path":"/gxfvtq5eYiClS2X7hxAAPBNrbWA.jpg","original_title":"पीके","original_language":"hi"},{"id":11324,"adult":false,"title":"Shutter Island","video":false,"overview":"World War II soldier-turned-U.S. Marshal Teddy Daniels investigates the disappearance of a patient from a hospital for the criminally insane, but his efforts are compromised by troubling visions and a mysterious doctor.","genre_ids":[18,53,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":14.6244,"vote_count":25460,"poster_path":"/nrmXQ0zcZUL8jFLrakWc90IR8z9.jpg","release_date":"2010-02-14","vote_average":8.2,"backdrop_path":"/8xt8AMb1OKC63AdhNSaYBWxB4Iq.jpg","original_title":"Shutter Island","original_language":"en"},{"id":766