adre","original_language":"en"},{"id":1640296,"adult":false,"title":"Putin and Trump · Best of Enemies?","video":false,"overview":"Vladimir Putin and Donald Trump — one the President of the United States, the other the President of Russia. Two men at the pinnacle of global power whose relationship keeps the world on edge. One a former businessman, the other a former KGB agent. Both have been active in politics for years. What drives them? The struggle over a possible ceasefire — or even peace — in Ukraine brought the two together last summer in Anchorage. But the question remains: who wants what? And who is succeeding with what agenda?","genre_ids":[99,10770],"popularity":0.1359,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/pOgFgle3xF1l1nmsCNagUcT44Jt.jpg","release_date":"2026-02-22","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/wTZRVCLN6OG553VWwOd8Ld1J5X7.jpg","original_title":"Putin und Trump: Ziemlich beste Feinde?","original_language":"de"},{"id":38,"adult":false,"title":"Eternal Sunshine of the Spotless Mind","video":false,"overview":"Joel Barish, heartbroken that his girlfriend underwent a procedure to erase him from her memory, decides to do the same. However, as he watches his memories of her fade away, he realises that he still loves her, and may be too late to correct his mistake.","genre_ids":[878,18,10749],"popularity":11.7483,"vote_count":16054,"poster_path":"/5MwkWH9tYHv3mV9OdYTMR5qreIz.jpg","release_date":"2004-03-19","vote_average":8.091,"backdrop_path":"/jzZcW65MZQfAgvbEoX8EWCvlxpk.jpg","original_title":"Eternal Sunshine of the Spotless Mind","original_language":"en"},{"id":55,"adult":false,"title":"Amores Perros","video":false,"overview":"A fatalistic car crash in Mexico city sets off a chain of events in the lives of three people: a supermodel, a young man wanting to run off with his sister-in-law, and a homeless man.","genre_ids":[18,53],"popularity":4.7541,"vote_count":2847,"poster_path":"/A4lH22nlFF7MdalGfcvSrlC1ttt.jpg","release_date":"2000-06-16","vote_average":7.633,